Why : previous recursive splitting was happening with a length of 500 (to be under the limit of the BGE. But this limit was on token and not character, so I changed the fonction. Also before I was adding all the title/subtitle... to the content, in order to potentially provide more context to the retriever but I was using all the indications. After further examination, I found that there was a lot of redundancy and also some parts like title can mislead the subject in comparaison to the subsection. So to mitigate that I will only use, for now, the last hierarchical part (I have found that some parts can have like subtitle/subsection/subsubsection with no text behind and maybe for them, I will need to add all the parts but will be later
